  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Super Pump is a one-button game perfect for players who want a short and fun experience. In this runner game you control the environment, not the player.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>SIMPLE AND INTUITIVE GAMEPLAY</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3381970/extras/7a1843a771bcdebe26977bcb164141f1.poster.avif?t=1736895750\" width=800 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3381970/extras/7a1843a771bcdebe26977bcb164141f1.webm?t=1736895750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3381970/extras/7a1843a771bcdebe26977bcb164141f1.mp4?t=1736895750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pressing and releasing of space key determines the action your player takes. This  press and release mechanic is intuitive and fun to play. <br><strong> <br>AVOID OBSTACLES AND HAZARDS</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3381970/extras/b83bc8ff8151d58391ebf3abade73543.poster.avif?t=1736895750\" width=800 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3381970/extras/b83bc8ff8151d58391ebf3abade73543.webm?t=1736895750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3381970/extras/b83bc8ff8151d58391ebf3abade73543.mp4?t=1736895750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Test your timing and memory skills in avoiding many hazards throughout the game! <br><strong> <br>DEFY GRAVITY AND GO VERTICAL</strong> <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3381970/extras/09e3b94bc0c740006d29051a045ccc27.poster.avif?t=1736895750\" width=800 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3381970/extras/09e3b94bc0c740006d29051a045ccc27.webm?t=1736895750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3381970/extras/09e3b94bc0c740006d29051a045ccc27.mp4?t=1736895750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong></strong>Gravity matters until it doesn't. Expect surprise twists and turns as you play the game.<strong><br><br>13 LEVELS WITH ORIGINAL SOUND TRACK</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Levels were  designed based on the music to help players experience a state of flow.  <br> <br>Super Pump is perfect for players who want a casual, minimalist, easy to learn but hard to master runner experience.  Test your button pressing and memory skills.  Help an old man run through various obstacles to retrieve his dog. <br> </p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Super Pump is a one-button game perfect for players who want a short and fun experience. In this runner game you control the environment, not the player.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>SIMPLE AND INTUITIVE GAMEPLAY</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3381970/extras/7a1843a771bcdebe26977bcb164141f1.poster.avif?t=1736895750\" width=800 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3381970/extras/7a1843a771bcdebe26977bcb164141f1.webm?t=1736895750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3381970/extras/7a1843a771bcdebe26977bcb164141f1.mp4?t=1736895750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pressing and releasing of space key determines the action your player takes. This  press and release mechanic is intuitive and fun to play. <br><strong> <br>AVOID OBSTACLES AND HAZARDS</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3381970/extras/b83bc8ff8151d58391ebf3abade73543.poster.avif?t=1736895750\" width=800 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3381970/extras/b83bc8ff8151d58391ebf3abade73543.webm?t=1736895750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3381970/extras/b83bc8ff8151d58391ebf3abade73543.mp4?t=1736895750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Test your timing and memory skills in avoiding many hazards throughout the game! <br><strong> <br>DEFY GRAVITY AND GO VERTICAL</strong> <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3381970/extras/09e3b94bc0c740006d29051a045ccc27.poster.avif?t=1736895750\" width=800 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3381970/extras/09e3b94bc0c740006d29051a045ccc27.webm?t=1736895750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3381970/extras/09e3b94bc0c740006d29051a045ccc27.mp4?t=1736895750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong></strong>Gravity matters until it doesn't. Expect surprise twists and turns as you play the game.<strong><br><br>13 LEVELS WITH ORIGINAL SOUND TRACK</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Levels were  designed based on the music to help players experience a state of flow.  <br> <br>Super Pump is perfect for players who want a casual, minimalist, easy to learn but hard to master runner experience.  Test your button pressing and memory skills.  Help an old man run through various obstacles to retrieve his dog. <br> </p>",
